OL,3,CHow to avoid authorised push payment
OL,4,Cfraud as officials slash compensation
OL,6,FIt would have made the UK a global
OL,7,Fleader when it comes to incentivizing
OL,8,Fbanks and other financial firms to
OL,9,Fimprove anti-fraud measures.
OL,11,FThen earlier this month, a new
OL,12,Fconsultation on lowering the amount
OL,13,Fwas launched - and today came the
OL,14,Fannouncement that losses will only be
OL,15,Fcovered up to #85,000.
OL,17,FHow can you avoid APP fraud?
OL,19,FFraud is the most common crime in the
OL,20,FUK.
