OL,3,CHow to avoid authorised push payment
OL,4,Cfraud as officials slash compensation
OL,6,FThe bank industry's own trade
OL,7,Fassociation, UK Finance, says:
OL,8,F"Sophisticated fraudsters exploit
OL,9,Fmoments of vulnerability and stress,
OL,10,Festablishing authority bias and
OL,11,Furgency to deceive victims."
OL,13,FThe most common deceptions include
OL,14,Ffake bank statements, hacked emails
OL,15,Fand convincing phone calls.
OL,17,FIt's vital that consumers look out for
OL,18,Fany requests urging them to move money
OL,19,Fquickly due to an invented deadline.
