OL,3,CHow to avoid authorised push payment
OL,4,Cfraud as officials slash compensation
OL,6,FAlways question unsolicited calls,
OL,7,Ftexts or emails. Remember email
OL,8,Faddresses and phone numbers can be
OL,9,F"spoofed" to look like they come from
OL,10,Ftrusted sources.
OL,12,FThe best way to contact a company or
OL,13,Forganisation to check things is to use
OL,14,Fknown email and phone numbers such as
OL,15,Fthe one on the back of your bank card.
